graph TB
    subgraph TrustyAI["TrustyAI Explainability Service"]
        direction TB

        subgraph Core["explainability-core (Java Library)"]
            LIME["LIME Explainer"]
            SHAP["SHAP Explainer"]
            CF["Counterfactual Explainer"]
            PDP["Partial Dependence Plots"]
            Fairness["Fairness Metrics<br/>(SPD, DIR)"]
            Drift["Drift Detection<br/>(KS test, Fourier MMD, Meanshift)"]
            NLP["NLP Metrics<br/>(BLEU, ROUGE)"]
        end

        subgraph Connectors["explainability-connectors (Java Library)"]
            KServeV1["KServe v1 HTTP Client"]
            KServeV2HTTP["KServe v2 HTTP Client"]
            KServeV2gRPC["KServe v2 gRPC Client<br/>(Protobuf)"]
        end

        subgraph Arrow["explainability-arrow (Java Library)"]
            ArrowCodec["Apache Arrow Codec<br/>(Columnar Data)"]
        end

        subgraph Service["explainability-service (Quarkus)"]
            REST["REST API<br/>8080/TCP HTTP<br/>4443/TCP HTTPS"]
            Consumer["Consumer Endpoint<br/>/consumer/kserve/v2"]
            CloudEvents["CloudEvent Handler<br/>(Knative)"]
            MetricsScheduler["Prometheus Scheduler<br/>(every 5s)"]
            Storage["Storage Backend<br/>(PVC / Memory / DB)"]
            MetricsEndpoint["/q/metrics<br/>(Prometheus)"]
        end
    end

    %% Internal relationships
    Service --> Core
    Service --> Connectors
    Service --> Arrow
    Consumer -->|stores inference data| Storage
    CloudEvents -->|stores inference data| Storage
    MetricsScheduler -->|computes from| Storage
    MetricsScheduler -->|publishes to| MetricsEndpoint
    REST -->|uses| Fairness
    REST -->|uses| Drift

    %% External interactions
    ModelMesh["ModelMesh<br/>(Payload Processor)"] -->|POST /consumer/kserve/v2| Consumer
    KnativeBroker["Knative Eventing Broker"] -->|CloudEvents| CloudEvents

    Connectors -->|inference requests| KServeModels["KServe/ModelMesh<br/>Model Servers"]

    Prometheus["Prometheus"] -->|scrapes /q/metrics<br/>Bearer Token| MetricsEndpoint

    InitContainer["Init Container<br/>(ose-cli)"] -->|creates ConfigMap<br/>model-serving-config| K8sAPI["Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS"]

    Operator["TrustyAI Operator<br/>(separate repo)"] -->|deploys & manages| Service

    Client["Client / Dashboard"] -->|REST API calls| REST

    PVCStore["PVC Volume<br/>/inputs/data.csv"] --- Storage
    DBStore["MariaDB/MySQL<br/>3306/TCP"] -.- Storage

